Cell Towers In The United States

Inputs

This page aims to display cell towers in the U.S. as outlined by the Homeland Infrastructure Foundation[1]. Each circle represents a site with a cellular tower. You can click on any circle to see who the licensee is. Ive included the ability to toggle between States and tower height, made possible by crosstalk. There is a lot of data to start with so try to reduce the amount of data with the filters.

Project: Jowanza Joseph. Feel free to visit my blog or say hi on Twitter.

[1] Any mistakes or omissions are from the data.
